  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps: 12-13 Guests</strong></p>
<p>Set amongst the trees at the higher end of Plagne 1800, Chalet Perrier has a welcoming and traditional feel as well as stunning mountain views.</p>
<p>The spacious interior has been designed in a modern style, with comfortable sofas in the lounge area and clad in pine with exposed wooden beams providing a homely and welcoming feel. From the lounge balcony, there are delightful views stretching out over the valley below. Bedrooms are virtually all en suite and furnished to a high standard. On the ground floor you can relax and enjoy the sauna after a hard day on the slopes. For your convenience to get to the lifts each morning, there is a <strong>Free </strong>Inghams minibus to take you to the lifts of Plagne Centre - a 2 minute drive away.</p>]]></description>
